E-12 SHELF NUMBER IS NOT ENTERED.
E-13 SHELF NUMBER MUST BE NUMERICAL.
E-14 SETTING CODE IS NOT ENTERED.
E-15 SETTING CODE MUST BE NUMERICAL.
E-16 THIS SETTING CODE IS NOT FOUND IN SETTING M/F.
E-17 BARREL A IS NOT ENTERED.
E-18 BARREL B IS NOT ENTERED.
E-19 BARREL B IS LARGER AND BARREL A.
