E-34 ALL PROCESSES MUST NOT BE BLANK.
E-35 13 OR MORE PROCESSES CANNOT BE ENTERED.
E-36 ENTER THE REVERSED PROCESS AND DEPARTMENT IN ORDER.
E-37 THE REVERSED DEPARTMENT CANNOT BE ENTERED BECAUSE NO PROCESS EXISTS.
E-38 THE REVERSED DEPARTMENT IS NOT FOUND IN THE DEPARTMENT NAME M/F.
