E-40 Y -> WHEN LATER PROCESS IS LAN OR AOQ.
E-41 G -> WHEN LATER PROCESS IS LAN OR HAN.
E-42 A -> WHEN LATER PROCESS IS COQ.
E-43 F -> WHEN LATER PROCESS IS IOQ OR CRM.
